{"id":63265,"global_id":"www.uniwa.gr?id=63265","global_id_lineage":["www.uniwa.gr?id=63265"],"author":"11","status":"publish","date":"2021-05-26 11:44:20","date_utc":"2021-05-26 08:44:20","modified":"2021-05-26 11:45:15","modified_utc":"2021-05-26 08:45:15","url":"https:\/\/www.uniwa.gr\/event\/3rd-summit-on-gender-equality-in-computing\/","rest_url":"https:\/\/www.uniwa.gr\/wp-json\/tribe\/events\/v1\/events\/63265","title":"3rd Summit on Gender Equality in Computing","description":"<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-63268 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/www.uniwa.gr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/Screenshot-2021-05-26-at-11.40.55-AM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1172\" height=\"410\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.uniwa.gr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/Screenshot-2021-05-26-at-11.40.55-AM.png 1172w, https:\/\/www.uniwa.gr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/Screenshot-2021-05-26-at-11.40.55-AM-400x140.png 400w, https:\/\/www.uniwa.gr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/Screenshot-2021-05-26-at-11.40.55-AM-800x280.png 800w, https:\/\/www.uniwa.gr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/Screenshot-2021-05-26-at-11.40.55-AM-768x269.png 768w, https:\/\/www.uniwa.gr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/Screenshot-2021-05-26-at-11.40.55-AM-700x245.png 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1172px) 100vw, 1172px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>The 3rd Summit on Gender Equality in Computing, organized by the\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/acmw-gr.acm.org\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Greek ACM-W Chapter<\/a>, will\u00a0be held by teleconference, on July 2, 2021.<\/p>\n<p>\nThe Summit aims at promoting gender-equal access to the computer-related scientific frontiers,\u00a0encouraging and educating women and men in an equal way to achieve their goals and utilize\u00a0their potential in digital professions. The goal of the Summit is also to celebrate and disseminate\u00a0the achievements of computer professionals in a fair and gender-equal way.<\/p>\n<p>\nThe Summit aims to virtually bring together students, researchers and professionals in the field\u00a0of Computer Science to<\/p>\n<p>(a) present and share their achievements and experience in the\u00a0computing field,<\/p>\n<p>(b) discuss and understand the reasons why there is gender disparity in\u00a0individuals opting for Computer Science and Engineering,<\/p>\n<p>(c) consider and exchange views on\u00a0gender stereotyping in Computer Science, and<\/p>\n<p>(d) come up with incentives and measures to\u00a0reduce gender inequalities in the field.<\/p>\n<p>More Info at <a href=\"https:\/\/acmw-gr.acm.org\/index.php\/en\/gec21\">https:\/\/acmw-gr.acm.org\/index.php\/en\/gec21<\/a>\u00a0<\/p>","excerpt":"","slug":"3rd-summit-on-gender-equality-in-computing","image":false,"all_day":true,"start_date":"2021-06-02 00:00:00","start_date_details":{"year":"2021","month":"06","day":"02","hour":"00","minutes":"00","seconds":"00"},"end_date":"2021-06-02 23:59:59","end_date_details":{"year":"2021","month":"06","day":"02","hour":"23","minutes":"59","seconds":"59"},"utc_start_date":"2021-06-01 21:00:00","utc_start_date_details":{"year":"2021","month":"06","day":"01","hour":"21","minutes":"00","seconds":"00"},"utc_end_date":"2021-06-02 20:59:59","utc_end_date_details":{"year":"2021","month":"06","day":"02","hour":"20","minutes":"59","seconds":"59"},"timezone":"Europe\/Athens","timezone_abbr":"EEST","cost":"","cost_details":{"currency_symbol":"","currency_code":"","currency_position":"prefix","values":[]},"website":"https:\/\/acmw-gr.acm.org\/index.php\/en\/gec21","show_map":true,"show_map_link":true,"hide_from_listings":false,"sticky":false,"featured":false,"categories":[{"name":"\u03a3\u03c5\u03bd\u03ad\u03b4\u03c1\u03b9\u03b1 \u2013 \u0397\u03bc\u03b5\u03c1\u03af\u03b4\u03b5\u03c2","slug":"conferences-seminars","term_group":0,"term_taxonomy_id":301,"taxonomy":"tribe_events_cat","description":"","parent":0,"count":57,"filter":"raw","term_order":"0","id":301,"urls":{"self":"https:\/\/www.uniwa.gr\/wp-json\/tribe\/events\/v1\/cat